    "Currently the output format is MP3 due to compatibility issues; however, MP3 is less efficient in streaming at lower bitrates compared to modern codecs like Opus." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Currently the output format is MP3 due to compatibility issues; however, MP3 is less efficient in streaming at lower bitrates compared to modern codecs like Opus."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Saat ini format keluarannya adalah MP3 karena masalah kompatibilitas; namun, MP3 kurang efisien dalam streaming pada bitrate yang lebih rendah dibandingkan dengan codec modern seperti Opus."
          }
        }
      }
